      <div class="testimonials">
        <%= image_tag "quote.png", width: 16, :class => "quote_img_start" %> I was very curious how GoodUI Datastories would be. After receiving the first issue I can say that it’s a great piece of professional work. I was feeling like sitting right next to Jakub and Vlad while they prepared and ran the tests. It’s a great thing to have everything provided in such detail. ”
