      <div class="testimonials_seller">
        - <b>Tom Carter</b>, Director <%= image_tag "stars.png", width: 100, :class => "rating_stars" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="message_to_us">
      <%= link_to new_contact_path do %>
        Say few words
      <% end %>
      about us.
    </div>


    <div class="plan_text">
      Questions & Answers

      <div class="plan_text_small">
        Ask any question and we will answer them for you right here, <b>with the most popular first</b>:
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="q_and_a columns_2">
      <li>
        <span class="question">What is AviaTrading?</span>
        <span class="answer">AviaTrading is a monthly subscription through which we introduce your aircraft into the market. Use AviaTrading as a channel to promote your business or engage in brand awareness.</span>
      </li>

      <li>
        <span class="question">What plan do I choose?</span>
        <span class="answer">If you have one aircraft to advertise you need to choose Basic plan. If you want to start advertising two and more aircrafts, then you have to choose Premium plan.</span>
      </li>

      <li>
        <span class="question">Can I switch between plans?</span>
        <span class="answer">Yes, you can. You will retain the same billing dates. Unused portion of the old plan will be reflected upcoming month on the new plan invoice.</span>
      </li>

      <li>
        <span class="question">Will my subscription automatically be renewed?</span>
        <span class="answer">Yes, if you subscribe using a credit or a debit card, then you will be re-billed the same day each month untill you cancel subscription.</span>
      </li>

      <li>
        <span class="question">Will my profile and advertisements remain after I cancel subscription?</span>
        <span class="answer">Yes. You profile and advertisements will remain. However, you will need to subscribe again if you want to re-activate your subscriber benefits.</span>
      </li>

      <li>
        <span class="question">Is it safe to enter my credit card details on the site?</span>
        <span class="answer">Yes. All your card details are encrypted for maximum security whilst travelling over the Internet. Further, no credit card details are stored anywhere on our site.

</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="message_to_us">
      Got another question?
      <%= link_to new_contact_path do %>
        Ask us anything.
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="repeated_plans_title">
      Choose a plan that suit you and subscribe with all benefits
    </div>

    <ul class="repeated_plans">
      <li>
        <%= link_to sign_up_path(plan: @basic_plan.id) do %>
          <div class="repeated_plans_button">
            Subscribe for <b>Basic Plan</b>
            <span class="repeated_plan_small">
              max. one ad only $50.00 / month
            </span>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </li>

      <li>
        <%= link_to sign_up_path(plan: @premium_plan.id) do %>
          <div class="repeated_plans_button">
            Subscribe for <b>Premium Plan</b>
            <span class="repeated_plan_small">
              unlimited number of ads only $150.00 / month
            </span>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="unsub_anytime">
      Boost your chances to sell an aircraft right now. Unsubscribe anytime.
    </div>

